ok, here is one of the codes for spawning npcs, from autospawn.CFG

[/code]

[code] //------NpcID---CoordX--CoordY--Height--RangeX1-RangeY1-RangeX2-RangeY2-WalkType-Descrption [/code]
But the 28 dont fit into that..so what is it???
